data.description: This charming two-story home with backyard oasis and bright, open floor plan is what you've been looking for! 3 beds, 2 baths and 2816 sf provide ample space for everyone and with a bedroom and bathroom upstairs you will love the extra privacy. Recently remodeling brings those desirable modern touches while maintaining the home's classic look. Original hardwood floors run through the home and are a beautiful addition. The back patio is the perfect place to entertain or take a relaxing dip in the 8-person hot tub. Mature trees provide ample shade and the huge front yard provides endless landscaping opportunities! You must check this one out - schedule your showing today!
data.whatILove: The town and overall community that it is located in is a blessing to be in. The school is small and the teachers are beyond amazing. This home has plenty of space and and open floor plan. Great for entertaining and just enjoying your time relaxing.
